{"id":576104,"date":[{"year":1979,"month":2,"day":18}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"99","ytitle":"","mtitle":"感怀","ftitle":"","authors":["范琰"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"范琰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读周总理一九六一年在文艺工作座谈会和故事片创作会议上的讲话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字珠玑落玉盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行行诠谛散金光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘教春雨千林润，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岂有妖风百卉残。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人已渺，事难忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年浩劫恨茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝和泪华章捧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽化红莲万朵香。"}]}